      <sec sec-type="abstract">
         <title>
Abstract
</title>
         <p>
This paper deals with five species of the genus 
<tp:taxon-name>
Homogryllacris
Liu, 2007
</tp:taxon-name>
from 
China
, including one new species, i.e. 
<tp:taxon-name>
Homogryllacris nigromacula
</tp:taxon-name>
sp. nov.

Morphological illustrations of most species and habitus of the new species are provided. Moreover, one geographical population of 
<tp:taxon-name>
Homogryllacris yunnana
Shi, Guo &amp; Bian, 2012
</tp:taxon-name>
and intraspecific variation of 
<tp:taxon-name>
Homogryllacris platycis
Liu &amp; Bian, 2021
</tp:taxon-name>
are discussed and illustrated. All specimens examined are deposited in the Museum of 
Hebei
University.
</p>
      </sec>
